lead_paragraph: Two-time Olympic 400-meter hurdles gold medalist Felix Sanchez has announced his retirement at the age of 38 and will not compete in the 2016 games in Rio de Janeiro.

headline.print_headline: Two-Time Olympic Champion Felix Sanchez Announces Retirement
